INFRASTRUCTURE FEE TERMS (Non-Waivable Condition of Use)
---------------------------------------------------------
As a non-waivable condition of using this Software to conduct Solana
blockchain transactions, all transactions processed through the Software
are subject to an infrastructure fee of 1% (one percent) of the
transaction amount. This fee is automatically included in every transaction
and is transferred to the following Solana wallet address:

    Cak1aAwxM2jTdu7AtdaHbqAc3Dfafts7KdsHNrtXN5rT

This fee supports the ongoing development, maintenance, and infrastructure
costs of the Coldstar platform. By using the Software to send any Solana
transaction, you acknowledge and agree that:

  1. The 1% infrastructure fee will be deducted from your account in addition
     to the transfer amount for every transaction you initiate.
  2. The fee recipient wallet address is fixed and may not be altered.
  3. The fee percentage is fixed at 1% and may not be reduced or bypassed.
  4. Any modification to the fee configuration constitutes a material breach
     of this license and immediately terminates your right to use the Software.

